gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 129, Spurs 120
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Spurs, 129-120. DeAaron Fox recorded a season high 43 points, along with 8 rebounds and seven assists for the Kings, with Domantas Sabonis adding 27 points, 14 rebounds, and seven assists in the victory. Zach Collins tallied 28 points, eight rebounds, and five assists for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 2-0 in West Group C play, and 7-4 in the regular season, while the Spurs fall to 0-3 in West Group C play, and 3-9 in the regular season.
